description: Urouge is a pirate who hails from a sky island. Judging by the style of the wings on his back, he is most likely of Bilkan origins. He is one of eleven pirates who have been referred to as "The Eleven Supernovas" on Sabaody Archipelago whose bounties are higher than when the Straw Hats arrive, and is the one with the lowest bounty of the said eleven.
name: Urouge
